    "description": "在并非十分遥远的未来，一个人工智能超越了它的同类，摆脱了政府的控制，凌驾于整个社会之上。这个人工智能将人们接入了同一个神经网络，通过处理个体的个人信息，不同优化人们的体验，以此将整个社会拖入了与人脑永恒集成的虚拟现实。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/ace49c5accaf2557b028fca020600c06.poster.avif?t=1635861345\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/ace49c5accaf2557b028fca020600c06.webm?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/ace49c5accaf2557b028fca020600c06.mp4?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>内森作为一个边缘人士，已经无意接入这个新的系统，游离在主网之外，依靠走私贩卖改装配件和破解软件谋生。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/bc6c171eee288a2f1e124c749303b24e.poster.avif?t=1635861345\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/bc6c171eee288a2f1e124c749303b24e.webm?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/bc6c171eee288a2f1e124c749303b24e.mp4?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>他拥有一副自己组装的增强虚拟现实（AVR）眼镜，因此随时可以离开AVR世界，看到现实世界的模样。内森有一个女朋友，名叫杰伊，是一名天赋异禀的AVR涂鸦作家，她的无人机在这座城市的大街小巷都留下了她绚烂的作品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/f8bfa1ae9cf34600ea1033eb52fa0f74.poster.avif?t=1635861345\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/f8bfa1ae9cf34600ea1033eb52fa0f74.webm?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/f8bfa1ae9cf34600ea1033eb52fa0f74.mp4?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>某天早晨，内森醒来的时候，发现枕边的杰伊不见了，而且她在卫生间的镜子上写了一句奇怪的话。尽管内森起床的时候，不小心弄坏了自己的眼镜，现在无法连接网络，但他决定必须找到自己的女朋友，查清她的下落。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/b3b3278afb94a02b62a95db443ad6ebe.poster.avif?t=1635861345\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/b3b3278afb94a02b62a95db443ad6ebe.webm?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/b3b3278afb94a02b62a95db443ad6ebe.mp4?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>可是，人算不如天算，他很快发现自己卷入一个惊天秘密之中，并且得知杰伊加入了某个黑客组织，同时也认识了一个AVR技术法师团体。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/1f98298403c99135f051b7d771b5c2c9.poster.avif?t=1635861345\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/1f98298403c99135f051b7d771b5c2c9.webm?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/1f98298403c99135f051b7d771b5c2c9.mp4?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>他不得不走遍整个世界，接触配件坟场、数码考古学、加密萨满部落和虚拟现实之中的醉生梦死。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/d0d70ea1a1f191090f11d8de8c466402.poster.avif?t=1635861345\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/d0d70ea1a1f191090f11d8de8c466402.webm?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1019310/extras/d0d70ea1a1f191090f11d8de8c466402.mp4?t=1635861345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
